Package hr.fer.zemris.linearna

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractMatrix
    Class implements IMatrix interface and offers methods for matrix algebra.
    AbstractVector
    Class implements IVector interface and offers methods for vectors algebra.
    LinsAlgDefaults
    Class provides static factory methods for linear algebra.
    Matrix
    Class extendes AbstractMatrix and implements unimplemented methods.
    MatrixSubMatrixView
    Class is used to have live view on original matrix that is provided through constructor wtih given column and row escaped.
    MatrixTransponseView
    Matrix which is live view of given IMatrix reference.
    MatrixVectorView
    Class provides live view on vector as one column or one row matrix.
    Vector
    Vector implementation extends AbstractVector.
    VectorMatrixView
    Class provides live view on matrix as vector.
